channel.description:
I decided to read Mr Linksys' Tutorial, and I got the sword perfectly. I also got the thunderbolts' yellow colors perfectly too.

This is Mr Linksys' sword recolored with Zeus' thunderbolts on each side. In Greek Mythology, Zeus would grab the sword(no human can hold it because it's as heavy as a mountain) and shoot thunderbolts at his enemies at the side of it.

But in NameScape, the wielder CAN wield it, and all it will do is slash people and cause lots of damage. The sword is very powerful and strong. The sword is also acursed to whoever it wields, a punishment by the mighty Zeus.

